WHAT IS A FILE FOR:

lonewoman/:
       error_log.txt: Used for errors during the upload.
        fixTropes.py: Deletes all tropes from database then adds them all back. This shouldn't be used.
             keys.py: Never have used, should sync all keys from every document.
           manage.py: Doesn't need to be changed ever.
          README.txt: This file, used for help about the project.
          syncSQL.py: Sync files to the database during the upload process. This file is known to have problems. I never got around to
                  rewrittng it. If I did though the syncDocumentsAndAuthors is what will need to be rewritten. Primarily,
                  making it more informative and work better for any document.
      update_log.txt: The upload status file. Only positive info will show here.
   uploaded_file.txt: Used during uploading to identify which file is being uploaded.

lonewoman/citations/:
            views.py: Citations formating. (identical code can be found at bottom of lonewoman/views.py)

lonewoman/image_viewer/:
           models.py: Models for the database. These should be set in stone. Unless there is going to be new types data in database.
            views.py: This views file is typically for the image view to display the doucment images.

lonewoman/image_viewer/templatetags:
          scripts.py: Most likely won't need. It is used for getting the doc and XSLT formating

lonewoman/lonewoman/:
            forms.py: Used for the contact the editor form.
         settings.py: Settings for django. Most likely to stay the same except when transfered to the NPS
             urls.py: Url patterns for the site. Uses REGEX patterns. Each thing in <> is a variable passed to the method after the comma
            views.py: The bulk of the site. Browse, upload, and citations(same as the citation file almost)

lonewoman/maps:
            views.py: Views file for the maps. Used to render pages for the maps.

lonewoman/search:
            views.py: Views file for searching. Handles all the searches.

lonewoman/static: 
                    : All the sites CSS, JS, and static Images are found here.

lonewoman/static/lw_maps: 
                    : Images for the maps

lonewoman/templates:
                    : All HTML files will be found here. 

/lonewoman_content/XML_Archive/stylesheets/:
   applyRichText.xsl: Used for styling and formating documents. Has JS code in here that could be modified.

/lonewoman_content/:
         config.json: Config file for the LonewomanSync.jar
   LonwwomanSync.jar: Java program that downloads xlsx spreadsheet from google drive and uses the info on it to update databases.

/lonewoman_content/CSV_Archive/:
                    : CSV files used for uploading the places, people, etc.

/lonewoman_content/PNG_Archive/:
                    : All documents images will end up here. They are converted from PDF to PNG during upload using Ghostscript.

/lonewoman_content/tmp_dl/:
                    : Used to hold the google document while running LonewomanSync.jar

/lonewoman_content/XML_Archive/:
                    : All documents XML(TEI) files will be uploaded to here.
